description: Get the summary metrics for this AWS account.

parameters.name: SummaryMetricQueries
parameters.description: The list of queries to retrieve the summary metrics. (dict) --- The summary metric query object. QueryId (string) --- The id of the summary metric query. MetricName (string) --- The name of the metric. Dimensions (list) --- The dimensions of the summary metric. (dict) --- The required list of dimensions for the metric. name (string) --- The name of the dimension. value (string) --- The dimension's value. AggregationPeriod (string) --- The aggregation period of the summary metric. StartTimestamp (datetime) --- The start timestamp for the summary metric query. EndTimestamp (datetime) --- The end timestamp for the summary metric query.

nested_items.name: SummaryMetricQueryResults
nested_items.description: The list of summary metrics that were retrieved.

nested_items.name: QueryId
nested_items.description: The ID of the summary metric results query operation.

nested_items.name: QueryStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the summary metric query result.

nested_items.name: Error
nested_items.description: The error message for the summary metric query result.

nested_items.name: MetricName
nested_items.description: The name of the summary metric query result.

nested_items.name: Dimensions
nested_items.description: The dimensions of the metric.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the dimension.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The dimension's value.

nested_items.name: AggregationPeriod
nested_items.description: The aggregation period of the metric.

nested_items.name: StartTimestamp
nested_items.description: The start timestamp for the summary metric query.

nested_items.name: EndTimestamp
nested_items.description: The end timestamp for the summary metric query.

nested_items.name: Timestamps
nested_items.description: The timestamp of each aggregation result.
(datetime) ---

nested_items.name: Values
nested_items.description: The list of aggregated summary metric query results.

nested_items.name: Min
nested_items.description: The minimum of the values of all data points collected during the aggregation period.

nested_items.name: Max
nested_items.description: The maximum of the values of all the data points collected during the aggregation period.

nested_items.name: Sum
nested_items.description: The sum of the values of all data points collected during the aggregation period.

nested_items.name: Avg
nested_items.description: The average of the values of all data points collected during the aggregation period.

nested_items.name: Std
nested_items.description: The standard deviation of the values of all data points collected during the aggregation period.

nested_items.name: P90
nested_items.description: The 90th percentile of the values of all data points collected during the aggregation period.

nested_items.name: Unit
nested_items.description: The units of measurement to be used for interpreting the aggregation result.
